-MkYB5ETwVMLC0P3lcVy.text: The suspect was reportedly last seen fleeing southbound after stealing liquor.

-MkYBdLMOEzmQRVy-m_x.text: Police on scene confirm a man robbed the store while wielding a 8-to-10-inch kitchen knife.

-MkYBuQfcP43tSd6w-sA.text: He is described to be a Black man last seen wearing a camo jacket, black Levi pants, and grey or green high-top shoes with "501" written on them.

-MkYC87PW-PIjnUVOPxV.text: The suspect may have fled on a mountain bike, according to police.
